edu.iit.ir.simpledm.preprocess
Class Attribute

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--edu.iit.ir.simpledm.preprocess.Attribute
public class Attribute
extends java.lang.Object

Contains the name and type of the attribute, and AttributeStats and ItemInfo(label information). If the attribute is continuous and discretized, Discretizer will be added as a member.
